\b \cf2 \cb1 GPU monitoring 
\b0 \cf2 \cb4 \
\cf3 GeforceSensor.kext: \cf2 \cb1 \
\cb4 Enable the reading of the GPU sensors for NVidia 4xx, 5xx, ...10xx Series. Don't use with NVClockX.kext! Only one of it! \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb4 NVClockX.kext: \cf2 \cb1 \
\cb4 Enable the reading of the GPU sensors for NVidia 7xxx-9xxx Series. Don't use with GeforceSensor.kext! Only one of it! \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb4 RadeonMonitor.kext: \cf2 \cb1 \
\cb4 Enable the reading of the GPU sensors for ATI/AMD Radeon HD4xxx - 8xxx, R5-R9 2xx 3xx 4xx 5xx cards. \cb1 \
\cf3 \cb4 X3100.kext: \cf2 \cb1 \
\cb4 Enable the reading of the GPU sensors for Intel X3100 at 965M chipset. \cb1 \
\cb4 \
\cb1 \ul Install only extensions that match with your GPU! \ulnone \
