\b Motherboard monitoring
\b0 \
\cf3 F718x.kext: \cf2 \
For Fintek LPC chips. \
\cf3 ITEIT87x.kext: \cf2 \
For ITE LPC chip, usually for Gigabyte motherboards. \
\cf3 PC8739x.kext: \cf2 \
For SMC LPC chip. \
\cf3 W836x.kext: \cf2 \
For Winbond or Nuvoton NCT LPC chip, usual for ASUS motherboards. \
